name: NOT ME
summary: ！！NOTME has passed the APPLab review, and opened the test download channel! Thank you for your contribution to the game during the beta test ！！Eight adventurers will explore the mysterious island, but the ship has been damaged by the storm. The werewolves on the island had already killed the two adventurers and blended into the team. You must discover who the wolves are while trying to gather supplies and repair the boat.
